        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded mb-3">
            <p>Vee, could you kindly attach the copy of the paper you mentioned to this thread? I believe this is my paper, but the pages you are referring to do not seem to align with the version I have. I would like to share the paper to provide clarity on the topic being discussed and to give context to the conversation. To ensure that we are all "on the same page," it would be helpful for you to upload your version. Thank you, Steve.</p>
            <ul class="post-meta mb-0">
                <li class="post-date"><i class="uil uil-calendar-alt"></i><span>12-07-2024</span></li>
