        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded mb-3">
            <p>Steve, could you please attach the paper you mentioned in the thread? I may have made errors in the page numbers. The paper was shared in the AMP discussion. Here is the copy I downloaded for reference. Thank you. You can find the attachment comparing RCM and PMO in the file named comparingRCMandPMO2000(2).pdf, which is 903 KB in size.</p>
            <ul class="post-meta mb-0">
                <li class="post-date"><i class="uil uil-calendar-alt"></i><span>12-07-2024</span></li>
